<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Button styling */
        .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .token {
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h1>Assalam-o-Alaikum, {{username}}!</h1>
            <p>Apka account create ho gaya hai. Verify karne ke liye neeche diye gaye button par click karein:</p>

        <a href="https://health-mate-system-xc1s.vercel.app/verify?token={{token}}&email={{email}}" class="button">Verify Account</a>

                Verify Email
            </a>

            <p>Ye code sirf 10 minutes ke liye valid hai.</p>
            <hr>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">Agar aapne ye request nahi ki, toh is email ko ignore karein.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>